node.text:
💥 GIVEAWAY 💥

I finally found a drink that’s healthy and tastes amazing. Made from natural ingredients: Lions Mane, Rhodiola Rosea, Huperzine A, Selenium, Magnesium, L-Theanine & Caffeine from Green Tea.

Want a chance to win a pack of drinks?

Rules:
• Follow @drinkalchemy.co 
• Follow me @jon.reyes 
• Tag a friend in the comments

Picking 3 winners this Sunday night!

Whether you win or not, keep an eye on your health, fitness, and overall progression. That’s my focus, and @drinkalchemy.co has my back. 👊🏼

node.text: What an incredible morning. I’ve always pushed to learn more and be consistent. Today felt different. I’ve realized there’s a level of riding that’s far ahead of where I am now, which has motivated me to take things further. Grateful for my health and well being that keeps up with my progression. Thank you @marttikuoppa for helping me work toward unlocking my true potential. 🙏🏼 #flatland

node.text:
💥Big News💥Flatland Scootering is now part of the @isfscoot ! It’s been a dream of mine to have a chance to prove myself in from of the world and now I have another reason to push my progression. “Flatland Scooter World Championship” this December 🥇

#scooter #flatland #jonreyes
